Finally got the drop!  (with help from a pally and necro), and had a minor heart attack when I clicked the item and DIDN'T see &quot;Effect: Flowing Thought (worn)&quot; listed on it!
<br />
Ohmigod... they've nerfed it, or something!!
<br />
It WAS a flowing thought item, right?  Why have I wasted all this time trying to camp the spot - I got people to help me - I'm so embarrassed!
<br />

<br />
A few deep breaths later, I realized they have changed from calling it Flowing Thought, to &quot;Mana Regeneration: +1&quot;.
<br />
So it's still gonna work for me.
<br />

<br />
I'm a happy, happy bard this morning!
